# CoinGecko Demo API Key (FREE)
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Without a key: ~5–15 requests/min shared across your IP → 429 errors.
# With a Demo key: 100 requests/min → no rate limiting in normal use.
#
# Get your FREE key in 2 minutes:
#  1. Go to https://www.coingecko.com/en/api
#  2. Click "Get Your Free API Key"
#  3. Sign up / log in (free account)
#  4. Copy your Demo API key
#  5. Paste it below and rename this file to ".env"
#
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
VITE_CG_DEMO_KEY=your_demo_api_key_here
